responsibilities for research and teaching and learning who wish to develop
strategies and practices to support undergraduate students undertaking and
understanding the nature of research;
?? Staff engaged in educational and research development in universities, including
Academy staff in the Subject Centres and in Academy York, who support staff in
developing linkages between research and teaching;
?? Institutional and national higher education policy makers, including professional
bodies and those giving research grants, who are concerned to develop policies to
encourage undergraduates to become involved with research.},
